---
title: Smart Turkey Zucchini Meatballs with Couscous
description: The secret to these super moist meatballs is grated zucchini! You've got to try them! Alongside, herby couscous and a mix of zucchini, tomatoes and onions keep things fresh!

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
